EmailTemplate.name: HOS Thank you for coming
EmailTemplate.subject: St Andrew's Cathedral School Tour: Thank You!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
Thank you for coming along on our recent Head of School Tour. I hope you found the tour insightful and you have had all of your questions answered.
If you wish to apply for enrolment, the next step in the process is to complete and submit the attached Application for Enrolment form. We will then invite you in for an enrolment interview with myself, the Registrar, approximately 12 months prior to commencing at the school. Once we have your details on our database, we will keep in contact with you by providing links to our school newsletters and invitations to any relevant upcoming events.
If your application is for commencement within the next 12 months, please contact us for an immediate enrolment interview so you can be included in the intake for that year (subject to availability).
If you have any further questions, please feel free to contact any of our Enrolments staff on 9286 9500.
Tell us what you think! We would love your feedback on the tour - please complete this quick survey - https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/SACStour.
In the meantime, keep up to date with what’s happening at the School via our Facebook page and more videos on our official Youtube channel.
We look forward to hearing from you and thank you for considering St Andrew’s Cathedral School for your child’s education and development.
Regards
Regards
Bruce Perry Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
phone 02 92869507 email BPerry@sacs.nsw.edu.au
